{"tid":2513075,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港媽淘寶買烚奶樽機「中伏」突爆炸　機器現火花發熱位熏黑全屋跳掣斷電","createTime":"2021-05-02T08:32:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T08:47:17.000Z","uid":271829,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"85c36b080341ad8a0155c0ec5283989bef99de25","tid":2513075,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T08:32:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2945000/2947012/explore_thumb_20210502_ch_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2945000%2F2947012%2Fexplore_thumb_20210502_ch_1024.jpg&h=9c724ce7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 一名港媽從淘寶購入烚奶樽機，使用期間機器突爆炸現火花，更令全屋跳掣斷電。<br />\n<br />\n網購電器要注意安全，一位港媽日前從淘寶購入烚奶樽機，使用時卻發生爆炸，機器出現火花，發熱位燒至變形及熏黑，更導致全屋跳掣斷電，險生意外。<br />\n<br />\n使用期間突爆炸<br />\n該名港媽日前在Facebook群組「淘寶開心share」分享「中伏」經歷，指自己4月3日以268元人民幣（約322港元）從淘寶購入一部烚奶樽機，其後從事裝修的丈夫將機器插頭更換成三腳插頭。港媽指起初烚奶樽機能夠正常運作，但本月25日使用時突然發生爆炸，<br />\n&quot;用用下突然爆咗一下，勁大聲，我仔瞓咗都嚇到喊！&quot;<br />\n港媽指烚奶樽機當時出現火花，意外後機器發熱位燒至變形破洞及熏黑。從她上傳的影片可見，她將烚奶樽機插頭接駁至一個已發黃的拖板，其中一個插座熱溶及變形。她嘗試按顯示屏上的按鈕，但沒有反應，並在影片中以普通話向賣家表示：「燒毁了這裏，破了個洞」，要求賣家退款。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2945000/2947012/3_1024.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2945000%2F2947012%2F3_1024.PNG&h=9b2b81f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拖板有熱溶跡象。（影片截圖）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2945000/2947012/1_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2945000%2F2947012%2F1_1024.jpg&h=e0b5b9ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n機器發熱位熏黑。（影片截圖）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2945000/2947012/4_1024.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2945000%2F2947012%2F4_1024.PNG&h=e65887af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港媽嘗試重啟機器但不果。（影片截圖） <br />\n<br />\n全屋跳掣斷電<br />\n意外令港媽全屋跳掣斷電，她需向大廈保安尋求協助方能解決。她透過經歷提醒其他消費者，切勿胡亂網購電器，<br />\n&quot;我上傳畀大家睇，係想大家唔好中伏，避免遇到呢啲問題，可大可小！&quot;<br />\n帖文引來網民討論，不少網民勸籲，切勿因貪平而胡亂網購未經安全檢查的電器，尤其嬰兒用品及與食用有關的產品；亦有人留意到港媽使用的拖板十分陳舊，質疑拖板因未能承受烚奶樽機的高火數而引致意外。"},{"pid":"2ff34a89da736c2bd1d093fd6ee3cfacf0314f61","tid":2513075,"uid":79793,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T08:34:31.000Z","msg":"仲想開番部野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fec7fac0d4c31af01f59e413e8110ce184e9006f","tid":2513075,"uid":173326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T08:35:21.000Z","msg":"成蟲.jpg"},{"pid":"cf0668b59442df4f67ebeaad6cc68c85ff4c16bb","tid":2513075,"uid":5725,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2ff34a89da736c2bd1d093fd6ee3cfacf0314f61","tid":2513075,"uid":79793,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T08:34:31.000Z","msg":"仲想開番部野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T08:36:10.000Z","msg":"笑左, 智商到底有幾低<br />\n出完火花仲想著機"},{"pid":"7f853c7ce5e9ec1cefef1b5a7b2a666b415c069e","tid":2513075,"uid":378793,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T08:37:00.000Z","msg":"淘寶野正呀喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e01b4fe208a95f424def93473dde9d78fd74a7c0","tid":2513075,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T08:38:09.000Z","msg":"烚下烚下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77c6289019d894eede01ed848d1f80380e7bcde8","tid":2513075,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T08:38:12.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">從事裝修的丈夫將機器插頭更換成三腳插頭<br />\n</span><br />\n自己改裝過喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b349b07d60ef74bc45c2e4f529fa29e8a330fec",